data.description: Come check out this gorgeous home located less than 10 miles of Downtown Edmond! This open modern home is the perfect for anyone! The granite countertops, white cabinets, and island make this open kitchen pop! The master bathroom has his & hers vanities, with each having plenty of counter space, a large tub (with a beautiful backsplash surrounding it) and a separate tiled shower. The master closet has access directly into the laundry room which makes it convenient to transfer clothes! The laundry room has dark wood cabinets for storage. This home features a large fenced yard with a 16x30 shop, pool, and storm shelter. Our favorite part about the home is that the master bedroom is located downstairs with beautiful views! Come and see this one today! .88 Acres MOL
